Title: There Is an Antechamber
---
That temple in
which we usually
find our Lord
is where we
see him shining,
holy.
The intellect goes there.
But when we grasp him --
with fingers and hands?
(of course not) --
in the holy soul, our
birthright, then we really
meet him in the
antechamber.
